  "detailed_description": "Rumour has it that a Remote Village is inhabited by Zombified dwellers due to an Ancient Curse at the local Cemetery. Being skeptical, you travel by car to this Village to Explore and Investigate what is Truth and what is Myth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/e8dd6efff635779f69f52066043b9e41.poster.avif?t=1725107692\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/e8dd6efff635779f69f52066043b9e41.webm?t=1725107692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/e8dd6efff635779f69f52066043b9e41.mp4?t=1725107692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>By doing so, you will be confronted with local intrigues, ancient secrets, and unexpected events. Talk to NPCs for guidance and information, follow their advice or not, use guns or be stealthy, reveal their secrets, make your own wise Decisions, or perish foolishly to unknown Occult Forces.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/8fa66f08184509ea293d039ab47c91bf.poster.avif?t=1725107692\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/8fa66f08184509ea293d039ab47c91bf.webm?t=1725107692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/8fa66f08184509ea293d039ab47c91bf.mp4?t=1725107692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique Weapons System with real ballistics, manual bolt operation, dispersion, and ricochets (The same system used in Weapons Simulator).<br></li><li> Total Freedom and Multiple Endings according to your Acts and Choices.<br></li><li> 4 Different Endings with Variations and Achievements.<br></li><li> Interact with the World, find Food and water, read Documents, and Examine Objects.<br></li><li> Non-linear Adventure with multiple possibilities, creating a unique experience for each player.<br></li><li> SaveGame system to help explore multiple possibilities without having to restart the whole game.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/dca9a538d62ba7a4e5e0431fa086a256.avif?t=1725107692\" width=512 height=364 /></span><br><br>A Realistic and Atmospheric Non-Linear First-Person Dark Adventure Shooter with Multiple Endings and Total Freedom of Action.<br><br>Be wise, your acts have irreversible consequences.",
