> Total Freedom and Multiple Endings according to your Acts and Choices.<br></li><li> 4 Different Endings with Variations and Achievements.<br></li><li> Interact with the World, find Food and water, read Documents, and Examine Objects.<br></li><li> Non-linear Adventure with multiple possibilities, creating a unique experience for each player.<br></li><li> SaveGame system to help explore multiple possibilities without having to restart the whole game.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2640930/extras/dca9a538d62ba7a4e5e0431fa086a256.avif?t=1725107692\" width=512 height=364 /></span><br><br>A Realistic and Atmospheric Non-Linear First-Person Dark Adventure Shooter with Multiple Endings and Total Freedom of Action.<br><br>Be wise, your acts have irreversible consequences.",
